lead_paragraph: Michael Phelps failed to qualify for the 400-meter freestyle final, finishing 17th over all in his first meet since serving a six-month suspension.

abstract: Michael Phelps, back from suspension for drunken-driving arrest, fails to qualify for 400-meter freestyle final at Arena Pro Swim Series; other swimming news noted.
